<i>adverb</i>: 푹신푹신 [푹씬푹씬], 푸근히 [푸근히], 폭신폭신 [폭씬폭씬], 포근히 [포근히], 편히 [편히], 편안히 [펴난히], 설설 [설설], 살살 [살살], 따듯이 [따드시], 느긋이 [느그시] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푹신푹신 [푹씬푹씬]</dt><br>
<dd>softly; comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>매우 푸근하게 부드럽고 탄력이 있는 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>Of a soft and elastic feeling in a very snug way.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푸근히 [푸근히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozily; snugly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>꽤 두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 부드럽고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a quite thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 부드럽고 따뜻하여 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a feeling or atmosphere being comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 꽤 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In windless and quite warm weather.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭신폭신 [폭씬폭씬]</dt><br>
<dd>softly; comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>매우 포근하게 부드럽고 탄력이 있는 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>Of a soft and elastic feeling in a very snug way.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>포근히 [포근히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozily; snugly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 보드랍고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 보드랍고 따뜻하여 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a feeling or atmosphere being comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In windless and quite warm weather.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>편히 [편히]</dt><br>
<dd>comfortably; easily</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 괴롭지 않고 좋게.</dd><br>
<dd>Nicely without any trouble for one's body or mind.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>편안히 [펴난히]</dt><br>
<dd>comfortably; easily</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 편하고 좋은 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a relaxed and good condition in one's body or mind.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>설설 [설설]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gently; comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>물이 천천히 고루 끓거나 바닥이 고루 따뜻한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of water boiling slowly and evenly, or the floor being evenly warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. gently</dd><br>
<dd>머리를 좌우로 천천히 잇따라 흔드는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of slowly shaking one's head left and right in a continuous fashion.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>살살 [살살]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gently</dd><br>
<dd>물 등이 천천히 고루 끓는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of water, etc., boiling slowly and evenly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>바닥이 고루 더운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of the floor being evenly warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. quietly</dd><br>
<dd>작은 벌레 등이 소리 없이 기어가는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of a small insect, etc., crawling without making noise.</dd><br>
<dd>4. gently</dd><br>
<dd>조심스럽게 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner in which one moves something or does something carefully.</dd><br>
<dd>5. gently</dd><br>
<dd>머리나 꼬리 등을 좌우로 가볍게 흔드는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of lightly shaking one's head, tail, etc. left and right.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>따듯이 [따드시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>아주 덥지 않고 기분 좋은 정도로 알맞게 높은 온도로.</dd><br>
<dd>In an appropriate, pleasant temperature, which is not too high.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>마음, 감정, 태도, 분위기 등이 정답고 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a loving and comfortable state of mind, having such emotions or attitude, or being in such an atmosphere, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>느긋이 [느그시]</dt><br>
<dd>comfortably; in a relaxed manner; at ease</dd><br>
<dd>서두르지 않고 마음의 여유가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>With composure, not hurrying.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>